4. Total amount of taxes an entity is expected to pay or recover during the reporting period

- For financing costs, the relevant line item is "Financial Expenses."
- For systematic depreciation, the relevant line item is "Depreciation."
- For taxes, the relevant line item is "Tax Expense."
